      "post_id" : 42888433,
      "comment_id" : 72880182,
      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "This will only list certificates stored in the JDK&#39;s trust store which is similar but for a different purpose to a keystore (which was asked about). There is a good differentiation here: <a href=\"http://stackoverflow.com/questions/17935619/what-is-difference-between-cacerts-and-keystore\">http://stackoverflow.com/questions/17935619/what-is-differen&zwnj;&#8203;ce-between-cacerts-a&zwnj;&#8203;nd-keystore</a>."
