    "body" : "<p>There are also console certificate manager written as a single-file shell script (open-source):</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://dev.to/sfkulyk/writing-panel-manager-for-certificate-keystore-in-linux-shell-187b\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">https://dev.to/sfkulyk/writing-panel-manager-for-certificate-keystore-in-linux-shell-187b</a></p>\n<p>Can browse, copy, delete, rename and compare keystores.</p>\n"
