    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>If you get a warning</p>\n<p><code>Warning: use -cacerts option to access cacerts keystore</code></p>\n<p>then you may use this command</p>\n<p><code>.\\keytool.exe -list -cacerts</code></p>\n"
